The paper proposes a method for building a dense, semantically annotated 3D map in real-time, which involves SLAM, segmentation, and recognition. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) or Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper utilizes a specifically designed CNN to improve segmentation accuracy, which indicates a potential fit for the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with semantic annotation, which could also place it in the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-category.
